author: Written by: FOX8Live.com Staff
title: NWS: Tornado warning issued for central Lafourche Parish until 7
text:
LAFOURCHE PARISH, LA (WVUE) - The National Weather Service has issued a tornado warning for central Lafourche Parish until 7:30 p.m. Sunday.
According to the NWS, at 6:51 p.m. a severe thunderstorm that is capable of producing a tornado was located near Montegut or 11 miles west of Galliano. The storm was moving north at 30 miles per hour.
